* Log Streaming\nArchitecture
** Data Flow
***_ Databricks generates events
***_ Azure diagnostic settings
***_ Routes to Log Analytics
***_ Ingested into tables
***_ Query with KQL
** Event Types
***_ Cluster creation/termination
***_ Job runs & failures
***_ Notebook execution
***_ Permission changes
** Configuration
***_ Azure portal setup
***_ Platform admins configure
***_ Data engineers consume
** Requirements
***_ Premium plan required
***_ 15 min ingestion latency
** Benefits
***_ Centralized logging
***_ Single interface
***_ Cross-workspace queries
@endmindmap
